OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1772831512
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'proud father' who
OL,4,Cdied in alleged murder
OL,6,FMr Rogers, who was known to friends as
OL,7,F'Disco Dave', was a keen traveller and
OL,8,Fa regular golfer at the Vale Resort.
OL,10,FHis family said the proud father of
OL,11,Ffour sons was a "devoted" brother,
OL,12,Funcle, and "cherished" son.
OL,14,FHis partner, Abbie, said: "He was
OL,15,Floved by all that knew him. My person,
OL,16,Fmy forever, my best friend. We as a
OL,17,Ffamily don't even know how to begin to
OL,18,Fmove on without him. We, as a family,
OL,19,Fare now left with a hole in our lives
OL,20,Fthat will never be filled."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
