CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1772831512
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'proud father' who
OL,4,Cdied in alleged murder
OL,6,FMr Rogers died in hospital on Monday,
OL,7,F2 March, where he had been in a
OL,8,Fcritical condition since being
OL,9,Fadmitted following an incident on
OL,10,FSaturday, 28 February.
OL,12,FLiam Walters, 26, of Pencoed, has been
OL,13,Fcharged with his murder. He appeared
OL,14,Fat Cardiff Magistrates' Court on
OL,15,FWednesday, 4 March, and will next
OL,16,Fappear at Cardiff Crown Court on
OL,17,FThursday, 5 March.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
