OL,3,CTributes paid to 'proud father' who
OL,4,Cdied in alleged murder
OL,6,FDetectives investigating the alleged
OL,7,Fmurder are continuing their appeal for
OL,8,Finformation and anyone who may have
OL,9,Fbeen in the vicinity of Felindre Road,
OL,10,FPencoed, between 12.30am and 4.30am on
OL,11,FSaturday, 28 February 28, to contact
OL,12,Fthem, quoting reference 2600063517.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/4
